**CALC-C** **BUILDING DESIGN CALCULATOR --- STRUCTURE, STEEL FRAMES &
CONVEYORS**

*Designs portal frame structure, steel section sizes, roof, wall,
drainage, all conveyors, and complete electrical load schedule*

**Purpose**

Receives building envelope dimensions from CALC-B and the equipment list
from CALC-A. Designs the full structural building including portal frame
schedule, steel section selection, cladding specification, conveyor
network (count, length, rise, motor kW), and the complete electrical
load schedule for CALC-D.

