**CALC-H** **NPK RELAY CALCULATOR + S2 HANDOFF**

*Final calculator in the chain --- aggregates NPK across all three
streams, calculates fertiliser replacement value, writes S2 handoff
payload to Supabase*

**Purpose**

Aggregates the nutrient content across the three post-S1 streams (EFB,
OPDC, POS), calculates daily and annual NPK fertiliser replacement value
using estate pricing, and packages the complete S2 handoff JSON payload
that is written to Supabase and consumed by the S2 Chemical Treatment
Calculator, the NPK Value Dashboard, and the Plantation Intelligence
tab.

**NPK Relay Calculation Logic**

> N CONVERSION FACTOR: ALWAYS 4.67 --- NEVER 6.25
>
> FOR EACH stream IN \[EFB_out, OPDC_out, POS_out\]:
>
> N_pct_DM = CP_pct_DM / 4.67
>
> N_kgd = DM_tpd × (N_pct_DM / 100) × 1000
>
> P_kgd = DM_tpd × (P_pct_DM / 100) × 1000
>
> K_kgd = DM_tpd × (K_pct_DM / 100) × 1000
>
> AGGREGATE (3-stream total):
>
> total_N_kgd = N_EFB + N_OPDC + N_POS
>
> total_P_kgd = P_EFB + P_OPDC + P_POS
>
> total_K_kgd = K_EFB + K_OPDC + K_POS
>
> REPLACEMENT VALUE (Sinar Mas estate pricing):
>
> N_value_usd_day = total_N_kgd × \$1.50 (USD/kg N)
>
> P_value_usd_day = total_P_kgd × \$1.80 (USD/kg P2O5)
>
> K_value_usd_day = total_K_kgd × \$0.90 (USD/kg K2O)
>
> daily_value = N_value + P_value + K_value
>
> annual_value = daily_value × 330 operating days
>
> BASELINE COMPARISON (guardrail-locked --- deviation \>10% → DATA GAP
> flag):
>
> N baseline: 582 kg/day
>
> P baseline: 197 kg/day
>
> K baseline: 930 kg/day

